data.description: Nestled in the charming New West Side, you'll find an absolutely adorable 3-bedroom 1.5 bath home that exudes character and warmth.  This delightful residence boasts a host of features that make if a perfect place to call home.  Stunning hardwood floors, loads of built-in storage, spacious living room and a fully fence backyard w/covered patio are just a few highlights! Conveniently located close to downtown Longview.  This house offers easy access to shopping, dining, and entertainment, making it a prime location for those who appreciate the benefits of city living while still enjoying the charm of a residential neighborhood.  This home is waiting for you to fill it with your own memories.
